QuestData.Title: Rune Covered Tablet
QuestData.Description: You cannot make out any of the symbols on the tablet. Perhaps the priestess would be able to decipher the mysterious runes.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Rune Covered Tablet to Priestess Kyleen Il'dinare at Odesyus' Landing on Azuremyst Isle.
QuestData.RewardText: I can't read these runes but I know someone who can...
